{"tid":630993,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「原創」笑話，笑爆咀","createTime":"2018-04-16T05:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T09:45:18.000Z","uid":123335,"like":4,"dislike":100,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"4eaae36f6432d716b9c2675fc207b9b15f511a94","tid":630993,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:38:59.000Z","msg":"1. 牙買加 <br />\n<br />\n保特有一日去士多想買水，<br />\n士多老闆「你好 Where are you from ? 」<br />\n保特「我牙買加」<br />\n士多老闆「你想用牙買架（牙買加）？」<br />\n保特「Yes , what's problem ?」<br />\n士多老闆「唔好意思，唔接受牙作為付款工具」<br />\n保特「!@#$%^&amp;*(」"},{"pid":"ca557c66b0e21516c847785c3835bcbea116ad9c","tid":630993,"uid":164363,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:40:31.000Z","msg":"做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688c7135c7210f3b51d59a0d88c49ce61cfd0878","tid":630993,"uid":173853,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:40:44.000Z","msg":"好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be4efdf16b851204613c39b498d64f55bdb02e5","tid":630993,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":33,"score":-32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:40:48.000Z","msg":"2. 思捷環球<br />\n<br />\n有一日，李思捷去環遊世界，<br />\n第二日，新聞頭條「思捷環球！ 環遊世界，真識嘆！」"},{"pid":"45740974282418ef2aa54d991ab1bee12914a9fa","tid":630993,"uid":20815,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"多謝你為全球暖化作出貢獻"},{"pid":"f412aa53ab43ff47660b9080befe59c4b3c58f49","tid":630993,"uid":9266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"......."},{"pid":"f20da11bb200d3d6160857279d8346db81c2ca3f","tid":630993,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:44:05.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c49a8c155cee3eafc85758fe01a7949e2c7c62a","tid":630993,"uid":123335,"like":12,"dislike":14,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"3. 靚女唔柯屎<br />\n<br />\n正所謂「靚女唔柯屎」<br />\n所以我成日走去各大商場女廁門口大叫「全部都係醜女！ 因為靚女唔柯屎！」<br />\n我亦都會去各大院校既女廁門口，又大叫「全部都係醜女！ 因為靚女唔柯屎！」<br />\n通常都一片鴉靜，哈哈，因為默認左囉 <br />\n<br />\n點知，我琴日再係女廁門口大叫「全部都係醜女！ 因為靚女唔柯屎！」既時候<br />\n竟然有個女人回應我<br />\n<br />\n「我柯尿咋！」"},{"pid":"c90df57f443d969d05c138b6068cde0cc2ceb621","tid":630993,"uid":61607,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9449a45d51d088d2c5afb63306c77dacde04d99b","tid":630993,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:49:22.000Z","msg":"4. 速食文化<br />\n<br />\n時下好興速食文化，好興落Clubbing 玩ONS , Fd with benefits <br />\n志在有即時既快感 <br />\n<br />\n我同我既好朋友，嘆「唉，依家個社會真係好垃圾，充斥速食文化，又Apps 又Clubbing 落Bar」<br />\n<br />\n我好朋友「係呀  我仲有好多即食麵添  哈哈哈哈」<br />\n<br />\n我「!@#$%^&amp;*(」"},{"pid":"26951d70d89afb8ddd7496301698c826581463a5","tid":630993,"uid":150937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:51:02.000Z","msg":"大家冇野呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1831630e1dbc82d09c6720436e44f49e3ae36a98","tid":630993,"uid":46435,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:51:36.000Z","msg":"樓主係李力持？"},{"pid":"8ea49ebdb65e20b3e5904037674f57bc3b16e817","tid":630993,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:53:41.000Z","msg":"痾尿嗰個好丁屎咁derder，其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW加油，練下就會好笑架喇，我欣賞你呀下"},{"pid":"4efd99391d7e03062b33daacd91fe90a841d4c82","tid":630993,"uid":123335,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:54:22.000Z","msg":"5. 通菜街<br />\n<br />\n有一日，我同呀明去旺角行街<br />\n呀明問我「點解通菜街俗稱女人街？」<br />\n我反問返佢「知唔知咩叫你條菜？」<br />\n呀明「你條菜 = 你條女 ，做咩咁問？」<br />\n我「菜即係女人，女人即係菜， 通菜街即係通街都係菜，都係女人」<br />\n呀明「Oh Jesus」"},{"pid":"851ea1cda594d71052d85fb382d09bd80ee0c572","tid":630993,"uid":181112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:56:01.000Z","msg":"樓主受咩刺激黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75ad92177e19236c45cd64ca52c4e99bcf25085a","tid":630993,"uid":1637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:56:36.000Z","msg":"多謝樓豬提供笑話 好好笑thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25de0f7954c8103f9acfce73cd04aa08ea529885","tid":630993,"uid":45477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"唔好咁喪啦"},{"pid":"df2918eb1e29552383ca56582532fff0d7877c6c","tid":630993,"uid":153503,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/16/135855_c493d18f3628103278b702a71847baea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F16%2F135855_c493d18f3628103278b702a71847baea.png&h=22e33dc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd69ad8bd9958f2a20f9951f29424f3ac658b8f6","tid":630993,"uid":104885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"笑爆肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c39436aae523ee0d3f0b992aec81f1d3137a3e7","tid":630993,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:00:39.000Z","msg":"彪哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇波買咁好興致淫下詩作下笑話"},{"pid":"5c1c27013d2491772802588accf6edcb452bf327","tid":630993,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-16T06:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387d1f5b9ebb12db0da83007389d36750a00d4b0","tid":630993,"uid":17669,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"